                                                java.lang.String object,

        • Python sscws
        • IDL spdfssc
        Parameters:
        library - the client library to produce example code for.
        object - object identifier.
        startTime - start of time interval with data.
        endTime - end of time interval with data.
        Returns:
        example client code to retrieve data from the specified dataset using the specified client library.
